{"tid":141598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華自爆辭職因做得唔開心：去到一個點","createTime":"2017-03-03T04:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T08:52:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e8c4ab66dd8d037a0f2d0146a9a46151b3f995","tid":141598,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"特首選戰在即，候選人曾俊華接受《星島日報》專訪時直言，辭職時仍未有參選決定，又指辭職其中一個理由是「做得不開心」，被問到為何做了近5年才不開心，曾俊華則形容是「去到一個點」，覺得不能做下去。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華在訪問中指，辭職不是因為參選，有很多其他事情，其中一樣是做得不開心，但拒絕透露有甚麼具體事情令他堅持辭職。他又指當時距離《財政預算案》公佈還剩兩個月，相關準備工夫已全部完成，認為是適當辭職時機。曾俊華周五再回應報道指，「做每一樣事情都有起有落，是累積而來的決定」，不會再具體講解。<br />\n<br />\n他在訪問中又重申，參選決定對家人影響、社會影響也很大，是一個積累得來的決定，又指沒有人作出選舉決定時會估計自己會輸。被問及有何優勝之處，曾直言「樣樣嘢都好過佢哋」，強調自己在3個候選人中是唯一一個獲得跨黨派支持，又指特首面對5年施政，若沒有跨黨派支持「會出事」。<br />\n<br />\n他以梁家騮的醫生註冊條例為例，指「一個人玩六個月，玩到佢死，受害的只有巿民」，他認為要這些事停止，需加強溝通，有較好的關係達到共識。被問及對手有許多鐵票，曾笑言「鐵都可以熔」，又指從來不覺得自己是「Underdog」。"},{"pid":"552eb4a3ba563d9c39108fb4f075b43e90b28c9f","tid":141598,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170303&amp;guid=56378758&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170303%26guid%3D56378758%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77UjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=800d2ba3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170303%26guid%3D56378758%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=9199fb04\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170303&amp;guid=56378758&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"ab1662c9581f431009a4d556ae5569f9d1b6f2c1","tid":141598,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"Mk囝用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牙曾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6f877b043d50a34a892ea525454fd1d7fbe53a","tid":141598,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"梁家騮果期堅係豁左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b804797245c4eba504e1c99c69571881dee6543f","tid":141598,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"等睇未來5年香港豬喊苦喊忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dae0c5417df6f8b8f633a63f2755e0cda42140","tid":141598,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"屎屎屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}